<node TEXT="12 Sep 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_544481641" CREATED="1432079053679" MODIFIED="1437428621440" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110912b.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#00ffff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;The era of peace and tranquility is completed.... The Hoon Dok Hae era is concluded and finalized on 7.3 (2011) in the second year of Cheon-gi.&quot; This is our goal. &quot;Sun Myung Moon, 7.3 in the second year of Cheon-gi&quot; [Applause] The overall conclusion has been made centered on the numbers seven and three.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      (Reading page 74 of speech book) &quot;The ultimate purpose of the providence is done. The date I wrote here is the 3rd day of the 7th month of 2011. It says The era of Hoon Dok is completed and perfected 'To be perfected and completed' has been reversed, and the word &quot;be concluded&quot; is missing here.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
