    <p>
      &quot;It is God and His younger brother (mN: Lucifer) that created Adam and Eve. Nobody knew it. In the equal position with God (<font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#54616;&#45208;&#45784;&#44284;&#45824;&#46321;&#54620;&#51088;&#47532;&#50640;&#51080;&#50612;&#44032;&#51648;&#44256;</span></font>), (Lucifer) created Adam and Eve.&quot;
