<node TEXT="Jeongju (CHONGJU ), home town of TF and TM" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_975227295" CREATED="1433314217853" MODIFIED="1437867308606">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="02 Sep 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1778363501" CREATED="1433484829440" MODIFIED="1445160057921" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110902a.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      The land around Jeongju is God's fatherland and hometown.
    </p>
    <p>
      I know it was the training ground where I was to fulfill the way of filial piety and loyalty to Heaven during my youthful years, my twenties and thirties, in order to show how one could live in that place, which is the model of the heavenly nation and which I shall never forget. If you ever go to that training ground, you must submit to training. Do you understand? [Yes.] It is my hometown, the hometown of the father and mother. You should go and live there.&#160;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <span style="font-variant: normal; word-spacing: 0px; float: none; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; font-family: serif; line-height: normal; font-size: 23px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline !important; font-weight: normal; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; font-style: normal"><a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120123.pdf"><font size="3" face="Tahoma" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120123.pdf </font></a></span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span style="word-spacing: 0px; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; float: none; text-transform: none; font-family: serif; white-space: normal; font-size: 23px; line-height: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); display: inline !important; font-weight: normal; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; font-style: normal"><font size="3" face="Tahoma" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)">True Father's mother was Kyung Mo Nim, which means 'Loyal Mother'</font></span>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="17 Feb 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1173702768" CREATED="1438726181332" MODIFIED="1438726233780" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120217.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;It is <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#51221;&#51452;</span></font>(<font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#23450;&#24030;</span></font>/ Jeongju, where Father's hometown is) that <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#51221;&#52265;</span></font>(<font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#23450;&#30528;</span></font>/Jeongchak, which means 'settlement') of the True Parents of Heaven, Earth, and Humankind occurs. What does <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#51221;</span></font>mean? It is 'to be settled.'&quot;
    </p>
    <p style="margin-left: 0.79in">
      (Katsumi: In this context, Father relates <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#51221;</span></font>of <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#51221;&#51452;</span></font>and that of <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#51221;&#52265;</span></font>.)
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
