  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;From my childhood, the spirit world educated me. I wrote lots of poems and I wish I had them now. One day, I wrote three notebooks that had 70 pages each. My speech years ago we are now reading is nothing compared to what I wrote those days, which were not my words but the contents I received directly from the spirit world.&quot;
