<node TEXT="TF crossing a river in Seoul" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1024652071" CREATED="1433314255034" MODIFIED="1433314278311">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="23 Apr 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_94754733" CREATED="1433485990496" MODIFIED="1436965191233" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120423.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;When I came to Seoul and lived in the district of Heuk Soek dong, I didn't have a boat to cross over the Seo Bing Go and I had no friend. I cried every day. One day when I was crying under the willow tree on the sandy beach, one lady, who heard me crying for three days, gave me a basket of rice cake. I can't forget what I owed to her in Seoul that time. I am still clear where that the place is and can find it even I visit there at night.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="All ancestors came to see me, the small-eyed boy of Osan family" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_630127864" CREATED="1436434706764" MODIFIED="1436434741106">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="04 Dec 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_209871762" CREATED="1436434748736" MODIFIED="1436965376721" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111204.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;All ancestors came to see me, the small-eyed boy of Osan family. One day, a person only whose legs can be seen came to me. His upper body couldn't be seen and he walked to my house saying 'I came to see the small-eyed boy of Osan family.' My grandfather couldn't see him and only I knew he was there. If I add (such spiritual contents) there would be hundreds of the principle book. I know the spirit world more than anybody else and one must understand it clearly. <b>I saw with my eyes that there is heaven and hell.</b>&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
