    <p>
      &quot;Before I became 10 years old, there already was a rumor about me called 'Small-eyed boy of Osan family.' I was the boy who told 'Someone is coming from the distance and we should prevent him from coming and he will damage our village otherwise.'&quot; (mN:I think 'someone' refers to the Japenese)
    </p>
