<node TEXT="Jeong Joo public school at age 15" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_863524380" CREATED="1433679908297" MODIFIED="1433679923046">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="10 Jul 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_254188423" CREATED="1433679942213" MODIFIED="1436966077205" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110710.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;I entered Jeong Joo public school (mN:in 1935, when he was 15 years old), and there was a teacher that was an excellent graduate from Pyeong Yang Teacher Training College and was 3 years older than me. He was praised by the director especially for his lectures on Chinese philosophy, and was good at wrestling and sports. I wrestled him and beat him.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      I already knew from my studies at the library the contents he was teaching and so I said, &quot;I am only three year younger than you, and I feel embarrassed studying from you and so I will study at the library by myself.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Age 17 Jesus came and asked TF to be the substitute" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1005706636" CREATED="1433314629251" MODIFIED="1433314651934">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="09 Aug 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1345399414" CREATED="1433487150355" MODIFIED="1440494361030" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110809.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Who would believe that if I said that when I was 17 years old, Jesus came to me to ask to be a substitute for him? Were you there at that moment? That happened before you were born. You understand this through my teaching and the principle. I gave a sermon based on the principle.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="14 Sep 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_326163655" CREATED="1433487202194" MODIFIED="1433487225045" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110914b.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;On my 17th birthday, Jesus came to me saying &quot;Be my substitute.&quot; I said 'Who are you? I am the person who know the God of Night and the God of Day have been in conflict against each other. Who are you? Identify yourself.' Then he ran away from me. So I went to the spirit world to find and meet him, and said &quot;If I need to be so, why don't you tell me that you had been trained to be able to unify the God of Night and the God of Day! What is this?' Why couldn't he do that? It is because nobody can teach the foundation and will of True Parents.&quot; (Katsumi: this unprecedented comment on his encounter with Jesus started at 36 minutes and 33 seconds of the video clip of that day.)
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="19 Sep 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1692665313" CREATED="1433487238498" MODIFIED="1433487259461" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110919.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;When I became 17 years old in February, in Easter (Katsumi: Father mentioned both but it is not clear if there were two occasions), Jesus appeared to me saying 'The time has come. Therefore be my substitute and successor. Will you do what I said?' I said 'Hey you ghost, who are you?&quot; Why (did I respond such way)? I knew the God of Night and the God of Day had been separate, and I didn't understand why the third party (who is Jesus) came to me and gave me directions. He did not know I had been through that difficult issue I had to solve. I said to him, 'Who do you think I am?' Before I asked that, I said, 'Do you know where I came from? I know the God of Night and the God of Day have been separate and there were the fallen parents. Who are you? You are the third person (after the God of Night and the God of Day) and so I must examine who you are. Do you know there are the God of Night and the God of Day?' He said, 'Why do you ask me such a thing?' I said, 'Who knows the answer?' Jesus said, 'I do not know what your question means.'&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="30 Oct 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1297873646" CREATED="1434922969549" MODIFIED="1434923233787" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111030a.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      In February, when I was seventeen, Jesus appeared. I knew that when he was young, he was driven away when he should have been welcomed. That's why he came to me. Jesus had much pain in his heart for having died and for the fact that his wedding ceremony had not taken place. He told me that I was the person who would make Jesus' wedding happen. This is what he told me to my face. Jesus was in the prime of his life. He told me &quot;Yong Myung Moon, you have to prepare the venue, take the lead and bring me to it. Yong Myung Moon, you have to help me get married.&quot; Why? &quot;Because, Yong Myung Moon, you are the ancestor.&quot;... You should make a signboard and put it up announcing that among the citizens of a nation, Rev. Moon is the king of fighting spirit who digests the world.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="04 Dec 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_270732363" CREATED="1436434238053" MODIFIED="1436966375869" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111204.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;When I was 17 years old, Jesus came to me calling 'Mr. Yong Myung Moon. Let's go to receive the Blessing.' I said (raising his voice) 'Who are you, bastard! You are talking about the Blessing without knowing anything. Do you know the God of Night and the God of Day, you bastard?'
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      He replied 'I don't care what you know, but I appear to you because the time has come. If I can't, I can't help but continue until I find (someone else).'
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      (Katsumi: Father sounds rude to Jesus. But we need to keep in mind that Father implied before that when Jesus came to him for the first time, he was not sure if it was Jesus since he had seen so many spiritual beings.)
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="04 Jan 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_480121913" CREATED="1437170183833" MODIFIED="1437170206651" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120104.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;When I was 17 years old, Jesus came to me saying, &quot;Mr. Yong Myung Moon, let's go to the Blessing together.&quot; (Raising his voice) (I said) 'Who are you? The date and officiator for the marriage aren't decided yet and where do you go? You fool! Do you know the God of Night and the God of Day have been separated?' Today I am teaching you everything.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="29 Feb 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1132433211" CREATED="1439036958761" MODIFIED="1439037013431" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120229a.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      No holy son was from the West. They are from the East. The first holy son who came was Jesus, and which nation did he come to? He came to find Yong Myung Moon in Korea, our liberated homeland. <b>He built and crossed the bridge to find me</b>, Sun Myung Moon. I came to know Jesus at the age of seventeen.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="04 Mar 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_376841373" CREATED="1439211464337" MODIFIED="1439211504288" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120304.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Jesus' spirit appeared to a boy called Yong Myung Moon when he was 17 years old. He knew my name. Jesus said to me, 'Let's go receive the Blessing.' We met each other for the first time, but those were his first words to me. (Raising his voice) '<span lang="zxx"><font face="Gulim, sans-serif">&#51060;&#51088;&#49885;</font></span>, <span lang="zxx"><font face="Gulim, sans-serif">&#45320;&#45572;&#44396;&#50556;</font></span>! (You fool! Who are you?) Do you know the God of Night and the God of Day have been separate? How dare you come to me saying such a thing?' (Jesus said) 'I have been preparing this and there has been a person in my mind as your wife.' I was 17 years old, and didn't decide that time (<span lang="zxx"><font face="Gulim, sans-serif">&#45208;&#44208;&#51221;&#50504;&#54664;&#50612;</font></span>). Any boy who became 17 years old and hadn't thought of marriage, can't become a man. When they become 14, or 15 years old, they realize there is man and there is woman.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
