    <p>
      Even though I had a house, even though I saw my mother and father calling my name in search of me, I was unable to call out and go to them. I hid. It was exactly like the time when God was calling for Adam who felt they had to hide from God. When I passed the eighth stage of such a lifestyle, I had to cross a critical point that was heavy with many such circumstances. You have to read this history. Otherwise, you will not understand me.
    </p>
