    <p>
      Katsumi:.Shin / <font face="Gulim, sans-serif">&#49888;</font>/ <font face="MS Gothic">&#31070;</font>means 'God,' and Pyeon / <font face="Gulim, sans-serif">&#54200;</font>/ <font face="MS Gothic">&#20415;</font>means 'side' or 'convenience.'
