    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120325.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120325.htm</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      (Holding Shin Pyeon Nim) &quot;This is Shin Pyeon. Kook Jin's third son, and the fourth one will be Shin Ju, who will be born in May. Pyeon (<font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#54200;</span></font>/ <font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#20415;</span></font>) of Shin Pyeon consists of <font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#20154;</span></font>(human) and <font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#26356;</span></font>(again), and therefore, it corresponds to <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#51312;&#44397;&#44305;&#48373;</span></font>(<font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#31062;&#22283;&#20809;&#24489;</span></font>: restoration of the fatherland).&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
