<node TEXT="18 Jun 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1833471171" CREATED="1433558673757" MODIFIED="1446584688816" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110618.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;My two elder brothers died.(mN:TF is the third son,but <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120123.pdf">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120123.pdf</a>&#160; stated as second son) My younger brother, whose name is Yong Gwan, died when he was 8 years old. He loved his elder brother (Father) so much and (before he died) he said to me holding my hand, elder brother, I will die before you,&quot; and I cannot forget that. (Father holds back his tears) I loved him so much. My aunt gave me bread and I wanted him to eat it and I waited all night to give it to him, but he died without eating it. I cannot forget that.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="TF&apos;s brothers and sisters (youngest sister is Ho Soon)" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1039691406" CREATED="1433329351600" MODIFIED="1444034972921">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="21 Apr 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_735584141" CREATED="1433558730063" MODIFIED="1442440093729" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120421.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      My youngest sister &#54840;&#49692;(Ho Soon) in North Korea, who had her twin elder brother. Do you know that without having a twin of brother and sister in the family the Second Messiah can't appear? Her twin brother died of chickenpox when he was 7, 8 years old after he had suffered from it for one year and eight months. When he was dying, he said to me, &quot;Brother Yong Myung, I am going first (to the spirit world.) This is for the sake of you but also for our youngest sister to survive to the end in my family.' For the sake of my younger sister, my two elder brothers died too (mN:TF is the third son), and nobody knows where their graves are. After I accomplish the restoration of God's Fatherland, I need to make my family graveyard.&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      The only yougest sister left in 2012
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120418.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120418.htm </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120418.htm">
</a>    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;People whom I loved in my youth were all gone. My father, my mother, my brothers and sisters&#8230; There is only one left, my youngest sister in North Korea. She had a twin elder brother, Yong Gwan (<font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#50857;&#44288;</span></font>). Both caught chickenpox at the same time, and she survived but he passed away. He truly loved my youngest sister. He was 7, 8 years old then and said to me '<font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#54805;&#45784;</span></font>, (brother) I think I will have to die soon for my younger sister.&quot; I said, 'Don't say such a thing carelessly.' My family went through such a course.&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="Younger brother &#xc6a9;&#xad00; (Yong Gwan)" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1635783992" CREATED="1442440003773" MODIFIED="1442440027497">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
