<node TEXT="Friend with a condemned man" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_964704750" CREATED="1433315010807" MODIFIED="1433315022568">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="21 Feb 2010&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_381825812" CREATED="1433720919797" MODIFIED="1433720940302" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon10/SunMyungMoon-100221b.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      When I was in prison, I became friends with a condemned man who was to be put to death the next day, so I learned what his father's heart was like. You cannot know what he feels until you are in his position. No one can know what the mother would feel unless you became her. It would be so difficult to meet someone, other than his mother, who would weep for him and say, &quot;I'll be put to death in your place.&quot; He had no such friends.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Prison friends liked to hear TF stories" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1505668993" CREATED="1433315022822" MODIFIED="1433329739320">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="21 Feb 2010&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1829532697" CREATED="1433720958948" MODIFIED="1433720982603" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon10/SunMyungMoon-100221b.htm">
