  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;When I was in prison, I said to people 'You came to prison because you stole this and that,' 'You don't have your father and mother,' or ''During the past 20 years of your stay in the prison, nobody has visited you.' They were surprised, saying 'How did you know that?' <b>I know those things because the spirit world informs me.</b>&#160;I said to them, 'If you follow me without dying, you will be saved.'&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
