</node>
<node TEXT="Work as an owner" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_77200893" CREATED="1437050781096" MODIFIED="1437050796804">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="00  2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1883656608" CREATED="1437050807239" MODIFIED="1437051015122" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120000.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      If you are going out to work as a day laborer, you must say to yourself, &quot;<b>I will work as an owner today</b>!&quot; Don't work as a temporary day laborer who was hired for the day. Knowing this essence of the principle, you work and forget, and <b>work to forget about your labor</b>. Then you will never get tired no matter how hard you work. I am now over seventy years old, but this has been my philosophy of life. I constantly want to invest more. Even though, my legs get wobbly, I want to give and invest more.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
