<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;Today is the special day when the proclamation of the restoration of God's fatherland must be substantially done. It is because the person who was ex-president of UTS (Dr. David Sang Chul Kim) passed away at an age of 97. Everything has been done centering on this day. As Jun Ho Seuk prayed, today is the 61st anniversary of my liberation of Heung Nam labor camp. (Then Father read his calligraphy given to Dr. Kim). I must open the door for him in the spirit world. &quot;<b>Congratulations! The establishment of the Fatherland</b>, centering on True Parents.&quot; It is True Parents that said &quot;The establishment of the Fatherland&quot; for the first time. &quot;Representative of loyalty and filial piety.&quot; &quot;Entering the Garden.&quot; It is the first time to use the word ___.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      Hyoyul (Dr. Peter Kim)! Do you know how important the message that I have given for the past three days is? ('Yes.') Those who were Blessed or passed away during this period when I proclaimed the inheritance of heavenly fortune, can stand on that foundation. He (Dr. David Sang Chul Kim) was originally a member of the Anglican Church and when I was founding HSA-UWC, <b>he was in the position of the representative of Christianity</b>. Those who were with me in those days are all gone. Mother was not there yet, Hyoyul (Dr. Peter Kim) was not there either. (Regarding HSA-UWC) Unification of World Christianity by what? Not centering on humans but by God's spirit. Then who is the owner of the Association? It is True Parents who are not fallen.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      For the past three days, I gave a very important message. Do you know that Hyoyul? ('Yes.') He passed away on that foundation at his age of 97. The 14th day of the 10th month are not odd numbers. What a scary day today is. Now it all depends on whether or not you accept my message. His wife is an amazing woman, who gave an education to her husband behind the scenes when he made a mistake in attending to me. Entering the Garden can't be done by oneself and one must have family.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
