      Father especially remembered and blessed sister Kathy Rigney who has worked in Africa for thirty-five years. Ms. Rigney had at one time caught malaria but she did not even go to the hospital. Instead, she continued her mission with only True Parents&#8217; providence in mind.
    </p>
