  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;Centering on Hwang Sun-jo, the President of UPF Korea, the Seunghwa Ceremonies for the realm of the tribal messiah and for the first, second and third Israels were to be completed between October and December 31, 2010. The three-day ceremony and indemnity stick ceremony (of the Blessing) are also to be completed.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      There appears a name 'Hwang Sun-jo' here, who is the representative and successor of the three generations, 19th to 21st generations from admiral Lee Soon Shin. He is also the president of the 'New Tribal Messiah Global Federation for Peace.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      Hwang Sun-jo! ('Yes!') Have you been conducting this (the Blessing, the three day ceremony, and indemnity stick ceremony of the Blessing)? ('Yes I have been doing it.') If not, that would be a problem. Hwang Sun-jo! Come to the front and pledge to do that. (Rev. Hwang asked the participants if they join him in doing this, and they said 'Yes!')
    </p>
  </body>
