    </p>
    <p>
      Sun Hae -- please educate the students well -- your husband cheated on you. Is there a man you would like to marry? I've see many get remarried -- I don't want to go that way. I want to make this blessing eternal.
    </p>
    <p>
      If I ask you Sun Hae -- to marry again -- would you do that?
    </p>
