<node TEXT="29 Oct 2009&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_989165719" CREATED="1434330731115" MODIFIED="1434837230816" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon09/SunMyungMoon-091029.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Three of these grandchildren were in the Sikorsky Helicopter Accident. The &quot;three musketeers&quot; (the three grandchildren) were not hurt. Shin Jun Nim cried out for King Daddy, King Daddy.&#160;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      Because I exercised I could make it. I was hanging upside down. I couldn't pull myself up or otherwise the seat belt couldn't be unfastened. It was a miracle that it didn't catch fire. After we got out then it caught fire.&#160;&#160;True Mother could have easily died. The trees all could have caught on fire. The pine branch that pierced the cabin had come close to True Mother's leg. We all survived.&#160;&#160;One special safety feature of this helicopter was that the gas tank did not explode.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="22 Sep 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1703675383" CREATED="1434330769881" MODIFIED="1434837226941" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110922.htm">
