    <p>
      You don't know the contents of the proclamation. It's a secret and it's regarding heaven and Eve.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="Entering the era where Satan&apos;s tradition, lineage and resemblance disappear" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_923948018" CREATED="1435612567686" MODIFIED="1435612634310">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="16 Nov 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_683528001" CREATED="1435612649262" MODIFIED="1444169340178" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111116.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;I belong to this and I am not beyond this. But by reaching the conclusion of the settlement of the True Parents, we are entering the era where Satan's tradition, lineage and resemblance disappear. The Kingdom of Heaven can be established on that principle on individual, familial, tribal and worldwide levels. All of you still resemble Satan's tradition and lineage. True Parents' sperm and egg have never met yet.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Wherever you are in the world, you read this speech" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_481067418" CREATED="1435614200526" MODIFIED="1435614207002">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="17 Nov 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1921645876" CREATED="1435614231225" MODIFIED="1445464863759" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111117.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;Anywhere I go, I ask what speech we read at Hoon Dok Hae that day and what impressed you when you were listening. <b>Wherever you are in the world, you read this speech (mN:below links) of the Cosmic Assembly for the Proclamation of the Settlement of the True Parents of Heaven, Earth and Humankind and the Substantial Word of God and get started with that day</b>. How can you go along with Heaven? There is the sun in the spirit world and in the physical world. Centering on the sun...&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon10/SunMyungMoon-100708.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon10/SunMyungMoon-100708.htm </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110305b.pdf">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110305b.pdf</a>
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Meaning of the proclamation of the coming of Heaven on 51st anniversary of True Parents&apos; Holy Wedding" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_217894195" CREATED="1433315334122" MODIFIED="1433315348393">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="18 Apr 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1295169285" CREATED="1433808150880" MODIFIED="1445501344955" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110418a.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      The proclamation this year(2011) was made at the 51st anniversary (2011-1960) of True Parents' Holy Wedding, so it was proclaimed in the position of overcoming the number 50. As Father says in his speech, &quot;I am leading a lifestyle befitting the era after the coming of heaven,&quot; the proclamation this time means that the victorious lifestyle of the Era After the Coming of Heaven will be expanded. In other words, it means the proclamation of the conclusion of the Era After the Coming of Heaven. Therefore, through the proclamation, the rapid cleansing of the sinful world will happen, and if we fulfill our responsibility through our practice, God's foundation will be dynamically established in an unimaginable speed and scale. We have entered into such an age. Then, let's think of our attitude in this age.&#160;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Cosmic Assembly for the Settlement of the True Parents of Heaven, Earth and Humankind" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_976215321" CREATED="1433025270970" MODIFIED="1433025299170">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="They are NOT my words" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_434207679" CREATED="1433317119260" MODIFIED="1433317134651">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="04 Oct 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_455918002" CREATED="1434158619464" MODIFIED="1434158634801" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111004.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Do you know how I am scared of that speech (Cosmic Assembly for the Proclamation of the Settlement of the True Parents of Heaven, Earth and Humankind, and the Substantial Word of God)? Those words are not something I said. I know that. Those are not my words.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="The speech given at the Cosmic Assembly" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1591264533" CREATED="1433317134916" MODIFIED="1433317146542">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="04 Sep 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1618251757" CREATED="1434158645891" MODIFIED="1434158775321" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110904b.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      The things I talk about dating back 70 years are the content you need to know. There is no need to talk about its merits or demerits. What are you going to do after calling for numerous people to gather from around the nation? I have made the teaching material for you. Did you come to hear me speak? This is a compilation of my speeches Do you have this in your home? Well? How many volumes do you have? Eh? <b>I don't think you have the speech given at the Cosmic Assembly for the Settlement of the True Parents of Heaven and Earth and Humankind and for the Proclamation of the Word of God's Substantial Self</b>. I had intended to give this on the occasion. We have tens of thousands of copies stacked in a large storage house. I hand these out when I go. Do not give it to those who are not here. I have made all of these already. They are all here. Are those who buy all the volumes of my sermons loyal servants of Rev. Moon? Can they become my children?
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110919.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110919.htm </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;You don't know that this speech Cosmic Assembly for the Settlement of the True Parents of Heaven, Earth and Humankind and the Proclamation of the Substantial Word of God came out after I, as the center, have established the realm in which full resonance in heart can occur at the same time in east, west, north and south in heaven and earth. The title of this speech means everything has been done.&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      (Opening page 74 of his speech file) &quot;Page 74 contains everything. You do not know what it says here. (Katsumi: the speech file the participants at ODP receive has 73 pages and Father recently added one more page to that.) The first thing is Perfection, Completion, and Conclusion. These are the ultimate purpose of God's providence. Then it says 'Eog Mansei,' which has the same value to it (which is 'Perfection, Completion, and Conclusion). Then it says Conclusion of the Reign of Tranquility and Prosperity. You do not know what Reign of Tranquility and Prosperity means. Hyung Jin said True Parents Eog Mansei. But where do True Parents remain? In the air? It should be In the Reign of Tranquility and Prosperity, True Parents Eog Mansei.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Each sentence in the speech of Cosmic Assembly for the Proclamation of the Settlement of the True Parents" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_905421792" CREATED="1433317146728" MODIFIED="1433317161640">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="28 Sep 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1612924000" CREATED="1434158792276" MODIFIED="1446711951035" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110928.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;<b>Each sentence</b>&#160;in this speech (of Cosmic Assembly for the Proclamation of the Settlement of the True Parents of Heaven, Earth and Humankind, and the Substantial Word of God) <b>corresponds to one of my speech books</b>.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
