</node>
<node TEXT="The meaning of &apos;Proclamation of the Substantial Word of God&apos;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_940328778" CREATED="1433315480238" MODIFIED="1433315492321">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="15 Sep 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_89704906" CREATED="1433809398979" MODIFIED="1437775774274" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110915.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;The Liberation of God. Why? God has not been settled yet. (Reading the title of his speech) Settlement of the True Parents of Heaven, Earth and Humankind.' This means everything. Then Proclamation of the Substantial Word of God.' This means the truth proclaimed by True Parents as the substantial beings who have been settled. What is the content of the proclamation? It is the ideal of family and nation. Then comes 'Cosmic Assembly.' This means this is the assembly that all people in the past, present and the future like to participate in.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="Humankind represents two persons" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1169588145" CREATED="1433315361437" MODIFIED="1434372389684">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="31 Aug 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1838048460" CREATED="1433808300617" MODIFIED="1433808321421" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110831.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;You do not know how precious these words are. There are lots of secrets here. This (speech) is like my daily. Look at page 51 (holding a sheet of page 51 and 52). Can you see this? ('Yes') It says 'Proclamation of the Era of the Parents of Heaven, Earth, and Humankind. Humankind represents two persons and if not humankind, restoration or religion would not have been necessary. There had not been parents, owners in heaven and earth, and people did not know why they were born. By having? (Which is translated here as humankind) here, everything has been solved. This? means two people: a human of mind and a human of body.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="18 Jan 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_215070226" CREATED="1437775797158" MODIFIED="1437775820121" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120118.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;'<font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#52380;&#51648;&#51064;&#52280;&#48512;&#47784;&#51221;&#52265;</span></font>/The Settlement of the True Parents of Heaven, Earth, and Humankind.' This means everything has been done. Before this title, it was <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#52380;&#51648;&#48512;&#47784;&#52380;&#51452;&#50504;&#49885;&#44428;</span></font>/the Cosmic Sphere of Sabbath of the True Parents of Heaven and Earth, which didn't have <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#51064;</span></font>(Humankind). <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#49892;&#52404;&#47568;&#50432;</span></font>(Substantial Word of God) is something you must be able to enjoy more than your breakfast, lunch and dinner. Have you been intoxicated with it even if you didn't eat breakfast, lunch and dinner and couldn't sleep at night?&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="07 Feb 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_601299032" CREATED="1438605653648" MODIFIED="1438605696229" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120207.pdf">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;<b>(Settlement of the True Parents) means they stand on the unified point of east, west, north and south</b>. '&#52380;&#51221; / Heavenly heart,' which transcends the past, present and the future, creates the cosmos of freedom where God is intoxicated with such a heart and doesn't feel shameful with no clothes on. That is the Kingdom of Heaven on earth.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Proclaim the era after the coming of heaven (April 18, 2011)" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_806932731" CREATED="1433315348624" MODIFIED="1433802262895">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="30 May 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_62963944" CREATED="1433808268341" MODIFIED="1445501146314" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110530.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      'I am proclaiming that all of you should model your life course on this path, become families that pledge to inherit and fulfill the will of God that True Parents have already accomplished, and be true to this pledge. On April 18 we celebrated our 52nd year of marriage.' 7 X 7 is 49 and 7 X 8 is 56. Between 49 and 56 what numbers should you have? There are 52 and 54 and nobody can steal these numbers.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      'On that occasion, I bought to a close the era before the coming of heaven, which was marked by sin and indemnity, and proclaimed the era after the coming of heaven through which a new heaven and new earth will be realized by returning to true love.' There is a distinguished boundary line between the two eras. Is it true or not? (Yes)
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      'Through this tour (European tour), I am leading a lifestyle befitting the era after the coming of heaven. Please engrave this point in your hearts.' You have to live the same life-style too.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
