<node TEXT="Difference between Seonghwa and Seunghwa ceremony" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_627785563" CREATED="1433315492624" MODIFIED="1433315505517">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="12 Sep 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1365969153" CREATED="1433809474253" MODIFIED="1440627325907" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110912b.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      That is why we have the Seonghwa Ceremony (mN:
    </p>
    <pre style="font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: normal; text-transform: none; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: -webkit-auto; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant: normal; font-size: 23px"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><span style="white-space: normal; font-family: Tahoma; font-size: medium"> &#32854;&#21644;&#31150;</span></font></pre>
    <p>
      ) for the new world. It is a strictly regulated rite performed on the national level. We have the Seunghwa Ceremony, but that is something performed after death. You need to know that from the moment you hear about these, you have the responsibility as parents to raise children who will go to the kingdom of heaven. The two ceremonies are different.
    </p>
    <p>
      The Chinese character for seong in seonghwa contains the character for yi &quot;ear&quot; and the character for gu &quot;mouth.&quot; This signifies that you should not lie to the world with your eyes, nose, mouth, ears, head, chest, stomach, reproductive organs and legs. You should not tell lies.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="15 Oct 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_303080812" CREATED="1433854468822" MODIFIED="1440626983965" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111015.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
