<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      I changed the Seunghwa ceremony to the Seonghwa ceremony. The Seunghwa ceremony should be done within three days after one died, which decides if they go to heaven or hell. The Seonghwa ceremony (starts) when the heavenly sperm is implanted in the ovum. You know that you couldn't find the journey of heavenly sperm but you have lived as you wanted.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="Seonghwa ceremony - One enters God&apos;s Kingdom" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_758869925" CREATED="1433457938672" MODIFIED="1433457944958">
