<node TEXT="26 Oct 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_339175265" CREATED="1434576665596" MODIFIED="1445549375050" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111026.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      (Opening the page <b>33</b>&#160;of his speech file) When you see <b>page 33</b>, it says, All people of the Christian faith recognize that God sent His true son Jesus Christ to earth two thousand years ago to save humankind. However, Jesus suffered a miserable fate. The leaders of Judaism and the people of Israel were supposed to receive Jesus as the Messiah and follow him with absolute faith, absolute love and absolute obedience. They should never have allowed Jesus' crucifixion to take place. He suddenly left this world, leaving behind the words, &quot;It is finished.&quot; This is an amazing statement.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      Yet these words apply to spiritual salvation only, and he promised to return. Ladies and gentlemen, God quietly raised and prepared the Korean people over a period of thousands of years. After two thousand years of preparation, His labor has finally borne fruit with the Second Coming of Christ on the far distant Korean Peninsula. I realized this when I was <b>33</b>&#160; years old. The spirit of that age is vigorous and think how such a young man became earnest for the nation that is perishing. You can read of such circumstances on this page.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Page 39" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1268775080" CREATED="1434577154087" MODIFIED="1434577190782">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="26 Oct 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1495761663" CREATED="1434577207771" MODIFIED="1434577243210" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111026.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      The Path Humankind Should Take: Distinguished Guests, your Excellencies, Ladies and Gentlemen. The path that humanity must now take is clear. What would give you cause to hesitate in the face of D-Day? That Heaven has revealed through us, the True Parents? There are now only six hundred days remaining. Only 600 days left and what kind of heart do you think I have? Read this speech as reference for that. This is page 39 and so I was before 40 years old then. Descendants of the Goguryo dynasty that dominated the region for 1,000 years can't disappear. You should think of that. Heaven's blessings will be with you on your ambitious and busy course. Unless I die, I must spread the blessing.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
