<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2 style="font-variant: normal; word-spacing: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: normal; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; font-style: normal">
      10.7, by the&#160;&#160;2011 H.C.
    </h2>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      (Then Father opened his speech file) You can't say you understand the contents on page 74 where it says 'The ultimate purpose of the providence is done.' (Then he started to read the sub- header on page 61) Seonghwa Ceremony of the New World and the Establishment of the New World Federation of Tribal Messiah. These two are related to the end which is page 74.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      (Reading page 74) &quot;The ultimate purpose of the providence is done. The date I wrote here is the 3rd day of the 7th month of 2011. It says The era of Hoon Dok is completed and perfected 'To be perfected and completed' has been reversed, and the word &quot;be concluded&quot; is missing here.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      (Katsumi: Father usually says 'to be perfected, completed and concluded.' But on page 74, Father put 'to be completed' first and there is no 'to be concluded.')
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;To be concluded&quot; was done on the 3rd day of the 10th month (2 aug) of 2011, and that day was the foundation day of Korea. Only I know the meaning of this page. Nobody can say 'This isn't true.' You don't know the God of Night, the God of Day, or the fallen parents. I wrote these on page 74, which had been blank. You don't understand even if I explained this page. Even the God of Night, the God of Day, the fallen parents and the perfected parents couldn't accomplish it yet, and so I didn't include the word 'to be concluded.' Only I know the reason why that word is missing here. Only one person (which is Father) knows this. Those who think that this (contents on page 74) isn't true, come out and explain why.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="07 Nov 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_301701976" CREATED="1435322599729" MODIFIED="1435322708004" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111107a.htm">
