    <p>
      You should memorize all seventy-four pages' of my text within a single week. You should memorize it in a week and live according to what it says. You have to know to what level you have risen. Through the loving and affectionate relationships with your siblings, find many spiritual children who can make commitments. You should do this within your clan, do you understand? [Yes.] [Applause] [True Parents thank you, we love you.]&#160;
    </p>
