    <p>
      (Taking out his two notebooks from his speech binder) &quot;These are my notebooks. This (bigger one) is the famous notebook from Las Vegas. This one (smaller one that Father has used since 2001) is black. This (bigger one) is not red nor green, but shiny as if it embraced the whole, and this is heavy. The size of the smaller one is 3/5th of the bigger one, which doesn't just happen.&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
