    <p>
      &quot;This notebook has all the maps in Heaven and earth. I will read the first page of this notebook for you. I used this notebook upside down and began to use it starting from the last page. The place where I put these photos is here (between the last and the next pages). This notebook has the history of Cheon If Guk. It says 'Oct. 3, 2001,' is when history started. (Raising his voice) What is that day? Then it says 'From May 4, 2009 and May 6, 2009,' during which things must be changed. (Showing the inside of the notebook) There is no lie here.&quot;
