  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;I will be 93 years old and mother will be 70 years old next birthday which will be also our Blessing Marriage day. 2013 means 3013 and I removed 1,000 years.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <font face="Tahoma" size="2" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)">(Katsumi: Father once said &quot;'premillennialism' is a lie.&quot;) </font>
