      I have also received the first blessing and the second blessing. The third time will be the last. We have not received the blessing since we became the True Parents. True Parents' holy wedding will take place on our birthday. We were born on the same day as if we were twins.... What you should know is that True Parents' holy wedding should be hundreds of times grander than any celebration held by any king in the course of history.
