<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      (True) Parents have been preparing for the new Blessing, but you, after the Blessing, have been merely taking care of your own children without worrying about (True) Parents' children's death and life. The Blessing you received is not for your own sake but for Heaven, Earth and Humankind.
    </p>
