    <p>
      <font face="Tahoma" size="2" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)">'Don't you know that you are the central person? I will wait until you come to realize that.' Before the God of Night and God of Day can be joined, I must conduct the third holy wedding ceremony of the True Parents. True Parents could not have their wedding ceremony yet.... The first and second have been held, and the third will be the final one. </font>
