<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="29 Jun 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_719853179" CREATED="1442527653958" MODIFIED="1442578724828" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120629.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;Why don't you register yourself? There are three stages of the registration: one needs to be registered at their birth and marriage, and to their nation when they are settled. Now Sedona here and Korea are one nation, not two, centering on <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#50724;&#49328;&#51665;&#51032;&#51312;&#44552;&#54620;&#45576;</span></font>(Father's nickname in his childhood, 'a small-eyed boy of the house who established the Osan school')&quot;
    </p>
