    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      The Seonghwa ceremony (starts) <font size="3"><b>when the heavenly sperm is implanted in the ovum</b></font>.&#160;You know that you couldn't find the journey of heavenly sperm but you have lived as you wanted.
    </p>
  </body>
