      &quot;<b>This is the palace where one can rest together with God, father and mother.</b>&#160;Take a look around this palace at day time, at night time and before dawn, and then you will understand there is no other palace like this. This is the only one palace. Yesterday evening, I was on the third floor and prayed. Until now, I've never breathed freely living here.
