<node TEXT="Korea Peace Dam" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1893608547" CREATED="1436218434045" MODIFIED="1436218471089">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="26 Nov 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1506792893" CREATED="1436218522623" MODIFIED="1436397477993" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111126.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Right after the meeting, True Parents left for the Peace Dam at Hwa Cheon. Father had said he must collect Jeong Seong from all places in Korea before leaving for Las Vegas. On Nov.25, starting at Nam Han River, they went up to Chung Pyung, and that day (Nov. 26), they went from Chung Pyung Dam up to the Peace Dam, which was established for the sake of protecting Korea from the flood attack by North Korean Im Nam Dam close to Geum Gang Mountain. At the Peace Dam, True Mother prayed and then True Father prayed for the perfection of God's fatherland.&#160;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Made mistakes twice or even three times" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_623157971" CREATED="1436397445768" MODIFIED="1436397505080">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="03 Dec 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1636441644" CREATED="1436397514764" MODIFIED="1436479338479" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111203.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;True Parents have been physically working but all was forgotten. Even though I proclaimed 40 years ago as you heard through the speech, Korea had damage after she forgot it. True Parents made clear how to become owners but you broke it and lived as you wished. How serious my sadness has been and how earnest I have been when crossing the summit once more after having proclaimed Korea becomes God's fatherland and homeland! You have to know how serious the responsibility is for those who run the country but have made mistakes twice or even three times.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="05 Dec 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1236961669" CREATED="1436479305034" MODIFIED="1436479336847" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111205.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      'God's fatherland and homeland. Where is it? Centering on Korean... Motive, process and results must be consistent in understanding and restoring the historical fact that Adam and Eve couldn't become True Parents. God's fatherland and motherland is that of Yong Myung Moon (Father's original name), the founder of the Unification Church, which realizes a delightful base of living with God by completing the ideal of family centering on one tradition and one blood lineage. This is the ultimate conclusion of today. (Father whistled.)&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="President" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_947505255" CREATED="1437137426751" MODIFIED="1437137435364">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="03 Jan 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1936177547" CREATED="1437137453210" MODIFIED="1437137568019" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120103.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      The nation and the (Korean) president (Lee Myung-bak) are the issues now. What I wish is that the president of this country, who can decide things, have the mindset to adapt himself to God's providence, but he doesn't have it. The issue is whether or not what they (he and his people) decide and want to do is still within the acceptable range. If they only want to do as they want, I must eternally cut off my relationship with them. If their <font face="Batang, serif"><span lang="zxx">&#51221;&#49436;</span></font>(Jeong Seo / <font face="MS Mincho"><span lang="zxx">&#24773;&#32214;</span></font>: love, emotion, feeling, sentiment) is more advanced than ours, we have to follow them, and if our <font face="Batang, serif"><span lang="zxx">&#51221;&#49436;</span></font>is advanced, they must follow us. There aren't two ways but there is only one way.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Dok Do (Dok Island) and Ulleung Do" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_958807012" CREATED="1436480013184" MODIFIED="1436480037766">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="05 Dec 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1190161462" CREATED="1436480081492" MODIFIED="1436480183494" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111205.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;Yesterday, I visited Dok Do (Dok Island) and Ulleung Do (Ulleung island). I thought Ulleung Do has flat land but I found it so complicated, where I went for the first time. It is full of turns and twits, which reminded me of the pioneering path of the Unification Church. Dok Do is a lonely island, and religiously speaking there is no other religion but Unificationism which is like Dok Do (lonely). (To Mother) What time did we come back? It was 5:40 p.m. and there was a great sunset at that time. I wondered how wonderful of a morning I would have the next day and I came here with such expectation.&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;It is only a 30-minute (flight) from Dok Do to Ulleung Do. Who will unite Father Dok Do and Mother Dok Do? Seeing Dok Do and Ulleung Do gave me the realization again on the commence and process of God' providence and history.&quot;&#160;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="10 Jan 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1378847930" CREATED="1437517395713" MODIFIED="1437517436220" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120110.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;Korea is God's fatherland and homeland. Why? It is because the True Parents of Heaven, Earth and Humankind were born there. If I decide it by myself and lie about it, I will die hit by lighting.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="God doesn&apos;t have His fatherland and homeland yet (mN: ???)" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1353782693" CREATED="1437603015898" MODIFIED="1437603073581">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="11 Jan 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1193956372" CREATED="1437603076005" MODIFIED="1437603146716" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120111.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;God doesn't have His fatherland and homeland yet. But you say you already have your homeland? This is a <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#49324;&#44256;</span></font>/ <font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#20107;&#25925;</span></font>/ accident. Rev. Moon has been fighting to correct this until now. I knew I would be able to have done 60% to 70% of my path, and before I die I need to solve the rest -- I don't know how many times I can hold the rallies until then --, and that's why I have provided you my text books and teaching materials and I tell you that you must live accordingly to them.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="No Old and New Testaments, nor the Completed Testament" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1307886146" CREATED="1438691552184" MODIFIED="1438691617315">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="13 Feb 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_619259735" CREATED="1438691624777" MODIFIED="1438691655602" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120213.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;From now on where will we go? There is the cultural sphere of Christianity and that of Unification Church, that is, Old and New Testaments and the Completed Testament. (There will be) no Old and New Testaments, nor the Completed Testament. Where do they settle down and continue? I have realized it is Korea and Korean people.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
