<node TEXT="Eve nation" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_557920880" CREATED="1435961593937" MODIFIED="1435961618960">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="24 Nov 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1971925388" CREATED="1435961688918" MODIFIED="1446932226585" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111124.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Who chose Japan as Eve nation? ('It is Father.') Nobody knows it(s background).
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120229.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120229.htm </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120229.htm">
</a>    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;It was me that decided to choose Japan as the Eve nation. Some Japanese secretly came to me asking, 'Are these your words?'' I said 'You will know it.' There were many people who visited me like that. I don't have time to be proud of such a thing. My sermons contain heavenly secrets.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
