    <p>
      &quot;What Japan insisted (during the WWII) was <font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#20843;&#32024;&#19968;&#23431;</span></font>(Hakkou Ichiu: all eight corners of the world under one roof / universal brotherhood). (Raising his voice) Who wrote Japan in Chinese characters as <font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#26085;&#26412;</span></font>(Nihon or Nippon. The Chinese character <font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#26085;&#26412;</span></font>means 'Origin of the Sun.')? It was Lucifer, who removed his Elder Brother, stole His words, and tried to eliminate the altar of the Moon tribe.&quot;
