<node TEXT="2,700 books of my speech have been published" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_862511788" CREATED="1433316966563" MODIFIED="1433316977785">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="02 Sep 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1714754593" CREATED="1434158427081" MODIFIED="1445724214254" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110902.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      As of now more than 2,700 books of my speech have been published. Today, we listened to my speech which was given 40 years ago, and how do those words can be valid yet still for now? It is because they came from heaven. Attend Hoon Dok Hae everyday, and even if all of you do not know these words, heaven will give special teaching to some of you regarding the topic of each day so that they can teach others.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110828.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110828.htm</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      &#160;
    </p>
    <p>
      I am now 93 years old and do not know when I will go to the spirit world, and in order to leave the tradition, I have prepared 8 textbooks and teaching materials.&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111207.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111207.htm </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      This fundamental problem hasn't been clear and so I, as a child, had so many experiences that you will never know and can't find them in this speech. Even in my sermons, I didn't mention them. Why? I keep them for the future. Only 500 books of my sermons have been published but there would be more than 3,000 (if all were published).
    </p>
    <p>
      Why do I have so many speeches and complicated contents? You have to know this. I am not a scarecrow.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Sermons contain heavenly secrets" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1715184532" CREATED="1438950525991" MODIFIED="1438950546420">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#0000ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="29 Feb 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1654552401" CREATED="1438950606349" MODIFIED="1438950670003" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120229.htm">
