  <body>
    <p>
      My sermons contain heavenly secrets. There will be 2700 books of my speeches if they are all printed, and as of now we have published only some 500 books. Before I go (to the spirit world), I think I must make clear what to print through my printing company. Hyo Yul (Dr. Peter Kim)! ('Yes.') Nobody is worried about it. Nobody. Nobody.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
