<node TEXT="Abel can exist only with the presence of Cain" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_386783202" CREATED="1443688969207" MODIFIED="1443688973829">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="02 Aug 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1238236157" CREATED="1443688981022" MODIFIED="1443689073416" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120802.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      But you must know Abel can exist only with the presence of Cain. Abel is necessary in order to restore parents. Abel is necessary in order to restore fallen Adam and Eve to the original status. Abel came to exist to restore the parents. If not for the fall, neither Abel nor Cain would have been necessary. Due to the fall, through the person called Abel, the parents must be restored.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      In order to restore relationship with true parents, Abel and Cain must be united and stand in such a position
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
