    <p>
      I shared about how Father often uses our bodies to pay indemnity during Hoon Dok Hae. And I paraphrased God's warning to Cain, &quot;<b>Why has your countenance fallen. If you can <font size="4">master your negative feelings</font>, won't you be accepted?</b>&quot;
