<node TEXT="Spirit Self" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_607197811" CREATED="1433318066543" MODIFIED="1433318083598">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="Who discovered Spirit Self" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_992221008" CREATED="1433318087222" MODIFIED="1433318100162">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="29 Oct 2009&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1872126409" CREATED="1434588845571" MODIFIED="1444555360947" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon09/SunMyungMoon-091029.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Who was the one that discovered the reality of the &quot;spirit self&quot;? Before True Parents there was never a concept of &quot;Spirit Self&quot;.&#160;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111121.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111121.htm </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111121.htm">
</a>    </p>
    <p>
      Yeong In Che (spirit self) is my original term. In any other religion, they say? (Hon: soul / spirit).&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120110.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120110.htm </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120110.htm">
</a>    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;It is Rev. Moon that invented the term '<font face="Gulim, sans-serif">&#50689;&#51064;&#52404;</font>./ <font face="MS Gothic">&#38728;&#20154;&#39636;</font>/ spirit self.'&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120422.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120422.htm </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120422.htm">
</a>    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;You know the word <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#54844;</span></font>(Hon: soul), do you? What is the difference between <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#54844;</span></font>(<font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#39746;</span></font>: soul) and <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#50689;&#51064;&#52404;</span></font>(<font face="MS Gothic"><span lang="zxx">&#38728;&#20154;&#39636;</span></font>: spirit self)?
    </p>
    <p style="margin-left: 0.79in">
      (Katsumi: Then Father said the following, which I do not understand)
    </p>
    <p>
      <font face="Gulim, sans-serif"><span lang="zxx">&#54616;&#45208;&#45784;&#51032;&#54844;&#51012;&#47784;&#47476;&#45716;&#44163;&#51008;&#50689;&#51064;&#52404;&#51032;&#44536;&#47548;&#51088;&#51077;&#45768;&#45796;</span></font>. (It means something like: Don't you understand God's spirit body is the shadow of spirits.)
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120422.htm">
</a>    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120422.htm">
</a>    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
