      &quot;You know the word &#54844;(Hon: soul), do you? What is the Difference between &#54844;(&#39746;: soul) and &#50689;&#51064;&#52404;(&#38728;&#20154;&#39636;: spirit self)?
    </p>
    <p>
      Katsumi: Then Father said the following, which I do not understand)
    </p>
    <p>
