    <p>
      This is not spirit self, but soul / spirit which does not have a character yet. You do not know what I am talking about. Satan does not know this either.&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;Here you have spirit self. Nobody has known this term, which I found. With your current spirit self, you cannot correspond to God, and cannot call him ___, which is not cannot go to heaven.'&quot;
