  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;Before the fall, was there a concept of east, west, north and south? Tell me what you think There are so many kinds of people here and I am here to inquire what kind of light color you are (giving off by) reflecting (God's love)? Yellow, white, red or black? You have your own color.&quot;
