<node TEXT="Breathe spiritually" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1780074229" CREATED="1433318155439" MODIFIED="1433318168907">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="15 Jul 2010&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1983489730" CREATED="1434589099732" MODIFIED="1444555680698" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon10/SunMyungMoon-100715.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      You must breathe, spiritually, every day. Just like you have meals daily, you must connect with God's word. You must place more emphasis on connecting with the word than eating daily meals. You must emphasize the word as most important. Only then will you walk the path to Heaven.&#160;&#160;How much will you nourish and grow your spiritual self, valuing God's word more than your daily meals.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
