<node TEXT="Hold on to God&apos;s word" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_161735295" CREATED="1433318194268" MODIFIED="1433318199194">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="15 Jul 2010&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1351188013" CREATED="1434589124840" MODIFIED="1444555716170" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon10/SunMyungMoon-100715.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Jesus said to Satan, &quot;It is written: 'Man shall not live on bread alone, but on every word that comes from the mouth of God.'&quot;(Matthew 4:4) This is very real. Have I lived until now because I labored? Or have I lived because of money? It is neither. I have lived by holding on to God's word. As you see, I did not perish.
    </p>
