      Father said one must find the best time for prayer and pray at that time because the time zone for the prayer is different from each other. Father also said one must pray with absolute faith, and prayer is like a root which must be planted deeply and doesn't appear in public. Father said if one leads a life of faith such way, they will have premonitions of what will happen that day.
