  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;It isn't necessary in living our daily lives to experience the extrasensory world by becoming spiritual or receiving revelations. I would like to say it is more difficult than anything else to systematize the facts behind such experiences and connect them to our daily lives. A spiritual phenomenon is ephemeral, but the truth is eternal.&quot;
