    <p>
      The time is coming when Heaven would protect even Lucifer, a monster, who brought countless people to hell through all kinds of diseases, and there will be no paradise nor heaven. Original creator of mind and body has passed the level of the warning of not to eat of the fruits of the tree of good and evil. You are now living in such era and so I hope you live your single-minded life with my words so that you can directly experience and understand what is realized in this speech. Your mind and body would be able to go to and come back from the level of the number 13, and you should make your family humble enough to receive such grace.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
