<node TEXT="Tree of Knowledge of Good and Evil" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_368593633" CREATED="1433318287369" MODIFIED="1433318305734">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="03 Aug 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_350593416" CREATED="1434677909782" MODIFIED="1444556474415" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110803a.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      As of now, humankind did not know what the fruits of the tree of good and evil were. Do you know it? ('Yes') How do you know it? When you read this speech, you can understand it within a week. Why did they say 'Heavenly Father' not did not know Heavenly Mother? It is because of their sin of &quot;eating&quot; the fruits of the tree of good and evil. If parents did not eat it (before their maturity), that would be the tradition through generations.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
<node TEXT="05 May 2012&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_724762200" CREATED="1441403560574" MODIFIED="1441403612998" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120505b.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;The Creator who created the whole cosmos couldn&#8217;t explain either what the fruit of the tree of the knowledge of good and evil is. Did Adam and Eve, who were there listening to God, understand what God meant by saying the fruit of the tree of the knowledge of good and evil? How about Lucifer, Michael and Gabriel? None of them knew about it. From the beginning of history until now, there has been only one person who clarified what it is. It is Rev. Moon.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
