<node TEXT="Harmony with Mind and Body" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_468261920" CREATED="1433318343766" MODIFIED="1433318352951">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="31 Aug 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1989637512" CREATED="1434805195288" MODIFIED="1434805210040" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110831.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &quot;Without achieving harmony, unification cannot take place. Unless your five senses function harmoniously, unification of your mind and body will never happen. Why do your mind and body fight against each other? Why? You do not know the answer. This is the fundamental problem. Why do they fight? Yours too, right? ('Yes') Then why? This is life-and-death issue. So far, there was no philosophical answer to this question and therefore, (humankind) has been in confusion.&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Unity of mind and body enables you to know what is going to happen" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1344624231" CREATED="1433318353227" MODIFIED="1433318363762">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="12 Jul 2010&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_785834490" CREATED="1434805233402" MODIFIED="1447104858972" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon10/SunMyungMoon-100712a.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#ff00ff" WIDTH="thin"/>
