<node TEXT="Dilemma of to say or not to say" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1995936521" CREATED="1433318889425" MODIFIED="1433318911459">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#00ff00" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="21 Feb 2010&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_749141368" CREATED="1434937251449" MODIFIED="1434937268641" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon10/SunMyungMoon-100221b.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#00ff00" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS" HIDDEN="true">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      I have a particular characteristic: if I go into a situation that isn't right, my mouth becomes dry. When I try to speak, my tongue gets stuck and does not move. What do I do then? What should I do? That is why I am hesitant about confronting difficult problems, lest I do harm to the nation's people. I don't know whether I am standing in such a position or not, but when I say in my mind that someone is bad, they will become bad. Supposing I were to say, &quot;He won't do well.&quot; Had I not said that, I could have at least harbored hope for him in heart, but having said it, what could I do if indeed that reality came about? You don't know how much responsibility I have.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node TEXT="Absolute sound" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1226372419" CREATED="1433318911690" MODIFIED="1433318940706">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#00ff00" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="TF able to listen to absolute sound since one and half years old" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1442663720" CREATED="1433318945593" MODIFIED="1433318955773">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#00ff00" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="04 Dec 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_1821363634" CREATED="1434937285492" MODIFIED="1437482589927" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111204.htm">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#00ff00" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Since I was one and half year old, I heard absolute sounds. After I became 12 months old, I came to see all kinds of spiritual things such as satanic spirits fighting against each other in the air. I said to myself, 'What is that?' Whenever I was fed on my mom's breast, a spiritual thing like a scarecrow and an animal appeared without fail which I could see only lower parts of the body. Then when I was one and half year old, I came to know absolute sounds.&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120405.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120405.htm</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;I am different from ordinary people. I can hear the absolute sound (&#51208;&#45824;&#51020;/ &#32118;&#23565;&#38899;). Even while I am sitting here, I can say (to anyone who is dozing) 'You are dozing, aren't you?' How can I know it?&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120109.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120109.htm </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon12/SunMyungMoon-120109.htm">
</a>    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;You can't listen to God's words but I can. The words I heard are the contents of my speech books which become textbooks and teaching materials for Hoon Dok Hae.&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111110.htm">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-111110.htm</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      &quot;Say Hoon Min Jeong Eum <i><font face="Tahoma" size="medium" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)"><b style="word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; font-size: medium; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; line-height: normal; font-style: normal; text-align: -webkit-auto; font-family: Tahoma">(mN:&#160;</b></font></i><font face="Tahoma" size="medium" color="rgb(0, 0, 0)">&#35757;&#27665;&#27491;&#38899;<i><b style="word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; text-transform: none; font-size: medium; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; line-height: normal; font-style: normal; text-align: -webkit-auto; font-family: Tahoma">)</b></i></font>&#160; , which means 'teaching the people the right sounds' and is the Korean script invented in 1443. The right sounds mean the absolute sounds.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      You haven't heard the absolute sounds, have you? When I was four years old, which is an even number, my great-grandmother appeared and taught me the song ___. When I became 16 years old, I knew, through her words, more than 88% of the secrets of my father and mother. When I was four years and 16 years old, she appeared to me saying 'You must learn the Hoon Min Jeong Eum, and listen to the absolute sounds.'&quot;
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      &#160;&quot;People of Hoon Min Jeong Eum can listen to God's words..&quot;
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
