<node TEXT="Won Mo boat  Gypsum Plaster Mold (Negative Resin Plaster Mold )" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_865807938" CREATED="1433326543132" MODIFIED="1433326552574">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#00ff00" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<node TEXT="18 Aug 2011&#xa;&#xa;" COLOR="#000000" STYLE="as_parent" MAX_WIDTH="600" MIN_WIDTH="1" ID="ID_861607761" CREATED="1435645907440" MODIFIED="1435646059800" LINK="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110818.pdf">
<edge STYLE="bezier" COLOR="#00ff00" WIDTH="thin"/>
<font NAME="SansSerif" SIZE="10" BOLD="false" ITALIC="false"/>
<richcontent TYPE="DETAILS">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Today you will be introduced to the Gypsum Plaster Mold method, which I devised, and participate in the launching of the Won Mo Boat, which was built using this and other new technologies. Beginning with the Cheon Jeong Boat, launched in Yeosu six months ago, Master Marine is opening a new global horizon in the shipbuilding industry and is contributing greatly to innovation in marine transportation in Korea and all of Asia, improving the quality of life for all
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      What is the Resin Plaster Mold Manufacturing Method?
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      In boat construction, wooden or FRP molds were utilized for building a boat hull and deck. This not only made the building process complicated but it also made the surface of the mold rough, compromising the quality of the outside planking and creating other problems. Resin Plaster Mold Manufacturing Method,invented by the Rev. Dr. Sun Myung Moon and perfected by Master Marine, Inc., solves this problem. This technology simplifies the process of boat building, reducing manufacturing cost and time in an innovative way.
    </p>
    <p>
      This has led to the popularization of ocean leisure Resin mold boat, lighter and stronger, invented by true Father
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110217.htm%20The%20boat%20twice%20the%20intensity,%20half%20the%20weight,%20and%20its%20boat%20building%20period%20will%20be%20reduced%20by%2030%25.%20They%20said%20it%20is%20Rev.%20Moon,%20who%20has%20been%20dedicating%20himself%20for%20developing%20shipbuilding%20technology%20from%201960's,%20that%20invented%20the%20resin%20molding%20for%20building%20the%20boat.">http://www.tparents.org/Moon-Talks/SunMyungMoon11/SunMyungMoon-110217.htm </a>
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      The boat twice the intensity, half the weight, and its boat building period will be reduced by 30%. They said it is Rev. Moon, who has been dedicating himself for developing shipbuilding technology from 1960's, that invented the resin molding for building the boat.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
</node>
</node>
