  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      How difficult it was for a foreigner (Father) to make a foundation in a foreign country. But here is a huge scale of work to be done. Here (in Las Vegas and the USA) will be the origin from which we can remove the world of ice at the North and South poles. Who will open up those areas and be responsible for the natural resources, including all kinds of fish? I can feel there are lots of fish here and that is our hope. This time, you realized there are lots of fish in the northern part of the Grand Canyon, didn't you? (Yes) There are not only fish, but also huge quantities of natural resources to develop in this backward region, which is bigger than Asia in scale, and when we really develop those we can conclude our activities and become the ancestors of the region.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
