    </p>
    <p>
      Now, on the foundation of True Mother victory (of indemnifying the disciples' rejection of Mary Magdalene by going thru the same rejection and accusation), the story of Jesus&#8217; wife can be revealed to humankind. Don Brown&#8217;s The Da Vinci Code enjoyed extraordinary popularity because the time has come to rehabilitate Mary Magdalene from obscurity. She was the predecessor of True Mother, and True Mother stands on the foundation of her devotion to Jesus.
    </p>
