    <p>
      &quot;(To have the) Relationship between parents and child means that they resemble each other. If children do not resemble their father and mother, it means they did not inherit the blood lineage from their parents, and also they did not inherit the parents' tradition. Tradition and the blood lineage must be the same (between parents and children).&quot;
